separate photo caption incorrectly spelled the name of Father Luis Olivares. 
</P>
</CORRECTION>
<GRAPHIC>
<P>
Photo, Father Louis Olivares speaks to organizing committee at the opening of 
the union's drop-in center. MICHAEL HAERING / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
