<P>
SPORTS RULES AND REGULATIONS; HIGH SCHOOLS -- SOUTHERN CALIFORNIA; PAROCHIAL 
SCHOOLS; CALIFORNIA INTERSCHOLASTIC FEDERATION SOUTHERN SECTION; HIGH SCHOOL 
ATHLETICS 
</P>
