<GRAPHIC>
<P>
Photo, Candidate Mourned Coffin of assassinated Colombian presidential 
candidate Carlos Pizarro is carried through the streets of Bogota after the 
former leftist guerrilla leader was killed by machine-gun fire aboard a 
Colombian jetliner Thursday. Associated Press 
</P>
